description: A little known fact about Mistress Irony, she is an art collector. She truly appreciates the finer things in life and she can spend hours contemplating her collections. When her newest piece of art, ends up in her dungeon, she never realized that her beautiful sub, Ava also has a fine appreciation for art. And when Irony catches her doing unspeakable things to her new acquisition, the fun really begins.
title: Art Appreciation
